## 🎨 DESIGN SYSTEM: "NOIR + CLAY"

### Colors
```css
:root {
  --bg-primary: #121212;       /* Charcoal */
  --bg-secondary: #1E1E1E;     /* Card backgrounds */
  --accent-gold: #FFD700;      /* CTAs, highlights */
  --accent-green: #10B981;     /* Verified/success states */
  --text-primary: #FFFFFF;
  --text-secondary: #A0A0A0;
  --border-subtle: #2A2A2A;
}
```

### Typography
- **Brand/Emotional:** `'Yatra One', cursive` — Logo, splash, headings
- **Functional/Data:** `'Inter', sans-serif` — Body, labels, metrics

### Clay Spacing (8px base grid)
| Token | Mobile | Desktop | Use |
|-------|--------|---------|-----|
| `--space-margin` | 20px | 40px | Page edges |
| `--space-padding` | 24px | 32px | Inside cards |
| `--space-gutter` | 16px | 24px | Between cards |
| `--header-height` | 64px | 80px | Top bar |
| `--radius` | 16px | 16px | All corners |

```css
:root {
  --space-margin: 20px;
  --space-padding: 24px;
  --space-gutter: 16px;
  --header-height: 64px;
  --radius: 16px;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  :root {
    --space-margin: 40px;
    --space-padding: 32px;
    --space-gutter: 24px;
    --header-height: 80px;
  }
}
```

