## 🦴 SKELETON LOADERS

Match exact card shapes. Show during first 2s load.

```css
.skeleton {
  background: linear-gradient(
    90deg,
    var(--bg-secondary) 25%,
    #2a2a2a 50%,
    var(--bg-secondary) 75%
  );
  background-size: 200% 100%;
  animation: shimmer 1.5s infinite;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
}

@keyframes shimmer {
  0% { background-position: 200% 0; }
  100% { background-position: -200% 0; }
}

.skeleton-video { height: 400px; }
.skeleton-meta { height: 60px; margin-top: 12px; }
.skeleton-actions { height: 48px; margin-top: 12px; }
```

